OL,3,CMurder accused appears in court after
OL,4,Celderly woman's death in fire
OL,6,FA man has appeared in court charged
OL,7,Fwith murdering an elderly woman who
OL,8,Fdied in a house fire.
OL,10,FJoshua Hodlin, 23, of Harewood Avenue,
OL,11,FPontefract, is accused of the murder
OL,12,Fof 75-year-old Shirley Hodlin.
OL,14,FHer body was found by emergency
OL,15,Fservices in a property at Yew Tree
OL,16,FWalk in Knottingley, West Yorkshire,
OL,17,Fafter reports of people trapped on
OL,18,FSunday night.
OL,20,FJoshua Hodlin appeared at Leeds
OL,21,FMagistrates' Court on Thursday.
